A 12 -year-old boy, Yusuf Badamasi, has been confirmed dead in open water at Kureken Sani, Kumbotso Local Government Area of Kano State, on Tuesday. This was contained in a statement issued to journalists by the Public Relations Officer of the Kano State Fire Service, Alhaji Saminu Yusuf. The PRO said, “We received a distress call from inspector Isyaku Aliyu at about 8:57 am. “On receiving the information, we quickly sent our rescue team to the scene at about 9:5am to bring the corpse out of the water. “Badamasi’s corpse was handed over to Inspector Aliyu Umar of Mariri police division.’’ Yusuf noted that the cause of the incident was still under investigation. He, however, urged parents to caution and stop their wards from going to the open water to swim.